price: (110) Who wants to expel you from your land [through magic], so what do you instruct?"
arabic: يُرِيدُ أَن يُخۡرِجَكُم مِّنۡ أَرۡضِكُمۡۖ فَمَاذَا تَأۡمُرُونَ
